Slide show Software for the FLOSS Manuals

Looks in the data directory of its project directory. 
Finds the config.xml file, which specifies the images name and duration.
Displays them in a loop on a black background.

You should create a data directory at the same level as the .pde file.
Put your images in the data directory and edit the config.xml file.

